{"tid":1785041,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應該點算好？（真人真事）","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T12:03:26.000Z","uid":322644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a33367b72de7fe284831cca2eb1feb51070897d7","tid":1785041,"uid":322644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"我個朋友（女）四十幾歲，有一個小朋友，就黎畢業。<br />\n佢老公六十幾，我呢個朋友同佢分房訓，食飯又各自各食，大家生活都係平淡。<br />\n佢突然同我分享，佢三年前識咗個已婚男人，三十幾，有兩個好細嘅小朋友。<br />\n呢三年都同佢好close,工作上仲會幫到下手。<br />\n佢再分享，三年前同呢個男人有咗，但聽佢話落咗個B，依家好後悔，佢覺得咩自己個肚嘅BB可以話冇就冇。所以佢有抑鬱證差唔多成幾年。<br />\n佢而家對呢個男人態度好差，但係曾經練左咁多年感情分手又唔肯捨得同佢分開，佢而家同我講要求個男人同佢老婆離婚，但佢老婆死都唔肯屋企人又唔比，因為怕兩個小朋友仲細影響佢哋成長。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家會有啲咩方法或者有啲說話比到我呢位朋友多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42385106ea23fb66d454e81dff08a95c18f90a6e","tid":1785041,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"班 狗 最 怕 我 哋 咁 做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd060ba323cbfa119349e587b4d6c2a4093f350f","tid":1785041,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br /